Same problem on android, the object file gpu_tracer.o contains the dummy function returning nullptr:

int __fastcall tensorflow::CreateGPUTracer(int result)
{
  *(_DWORD *)result = 0;
  return result;
}

and a "global":

int GLOBAL__sub_I__ZN10tensorflow15CreateGPUTracerEv()
{
  std::ios_base::Init::Init((std::ios_base::Init *)&std::__ioinit);
  return _aeabi_atexit(&std::__ioinit, std::ios_base::Init::~Init, &_dso_handle);
}
